
    NATIONAL Treasury has appointed Ian Stuart as the acting Deputy
Director-General for the Budget Office.Stuart is the current Chief Director for Fiscal Policy in the Budget
Office within the National Treasury.The appointment of Stuart follows the application of Michael Sachs for a
